2008-11-08 bitter 1.3 released

 * Added -q switch to omit filenames.
 * Added -c switch to convert SHA-1 between hex and base32.
 * Removed unused code.
 * Changed license from 4-clause to 2-clause BSD license.

2006-08-07 bitter 1.1 released

 * src/lib/tiger.c:
   * Fixed compile issue on Alpha caused by bogus macro definition.
   * Use the Alpha variant for all but 32-bit platforms. At least on
     x86-64 this variant is 20% faster as well.

2006-08-01 bitter 1.0 released

   * Initial release.
